         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>This fragment is too small to allow a ceramologic dating. Its lettering is very awkward. It might be rather archaic, hence at line 1
                    the beginning of a personal name in <foreign xml:lang="grc">Ἁγε-</foreign> or even <foreign xml:lang="grc">Ἁγη-</foreign> 
                    should not be excluded.</p>
